    <title>Installation of LFS-Bootscripts</title>

    <para>The following patch allows the RaQ2/Qube2 use the LCD Screen
    with the bootscripts:</para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i contrib/&lfs-bootscripts-raq2-patch;</userinput></screen>

    <para>Install the package:</para>

<screen><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

